## Identifying Windows Machines

These three ports together = Windows machine:

| Port | Service | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| 135 | MSRPC | Microsoft Remote Procedure Call |
| 139 | NetBIOS | Windows network sharing |
| 445 | SMB | Windows file sharing |

---

## Port 445 — SMB Warning

Port 445 = SMB = Server Message Block

Windows opens this automatically for file and printer sharing.

**WannaCry 2017:**
- Ransomware that targeted port 445
- Spread automatically to every vulnerable Windows machine
- 200,000+ computers infected in 150 countries
- $4 billion in damage

**SOC Action:** Always monitor port 445. Ensure machines are patched.

